            <head>A Looking-glaſſe, For Murtherers and Blaſphemers; wherein they <gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="1 word">
                  <desc>〈◊〉</desc>
               </gap> Gods Iudgement ſhowne vpon a Keeper neere Enfield C<gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="4 letters">
                  <desc>••••</desc>
               </gap> 
               <gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="1 word">
