               </gap> 
               <gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="2 letters">
                  <desc>••</desc>
               </gap>is was done on Monday night, the xii. day of Iune, being the ſame da<gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="1 letter">
                  <desc>•</desc>
               </gap> 
               <gap reason="illegible: page cropped" extent="1 span">
